    <release version="3.0.0" date="2025-10-24" type="stable">
      <url>https://github.com/Equicord/Equibop/releases/tag/v3.0.0</url>
      <description>
        <p>Complete Rewrite</p>
        <p>This is a complete rewrite from the ground up. The v2 codebase had significant architectural issues that made it unmaintainable, so we've rebuilt Equibop with a cleaner foundation.</p>
        <p>Major Changes</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Migrated from pnpm to bun for better performance and DX</li>
          <li>Complete code restructure for improved maintainability</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Known Limitations</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Some features from v2 are not yet re-implemented</li>
          <li>Report issues at https://github.com/Equicord/Equibop/issues</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
